column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid, p.ra, p.dec,  p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  p.score, p.type, s.class,  p.petroRad_u, p.petroR5#_u, p.expRad_u FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE  p.score > #  AND p.CLEAN = #  AND p.u BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.g BETWEEN # AND # ORDER BY field
